OL,3,CCar plant boss warns production could
OL,4,C'stop' without Government electric
OL,5,Cpromise
OL,7,FThe owner of vehicle-maker Vauxhall
OL,8,Fsays the next UK Government needs to
OL,9,Ffully commit to electric motoring to
OL,10,Fsecure the future of the company's
OL,11,Fplant at Ellesmere Port in Cheshire.
OL,13,FStellantis UK started electric-only
OL,14,Fvan production at Ellesmere Port in
OL,15,FSeptember 2023, and intends to
OL,16,Ftransition its Luton plant to build
OL,17,Felectric vans from the first half of
OL,18,Fnext year.
