OL,3,CCar plant boss warns production could
OL,4,C'stop' without Government electric
OL,5,Cpromise
OL,7,FBut the managing director of
OL,8,FStellantis UK, Maria Grazia Davino,
OL,9,Ftold an industry conference that a
OL,10,Fdecision on the future of both sites
OL,11,Fcould be made in "less than a year".
OL,13,FUnder the zero emission vehicle (Zev)
OL,14,Fmandate, at least 22% of new cars and
OL,15,F10% of new vans sold by each
OL,16,Fmanufacturer in the UK this year are
OL,17,Frequired to be zero emission, which in
OL,18,Fmost cases means pure electric.
OL,20,FThe threshold will rise annually.
