OL,5,Cpromise
OL,7,FUnder the rules of the mandate,
OL,8,Fmanufacturers risk being required to
OL,9,Fpay the Government #15,000 per
OL,10,Fpolluting vehicle sold above the
OL,11,Flimits.
OL,13,FBut ministers do not expect any
OL,14,Fbusinesses to face fines this year, as
OL,15,Fthey will be able to use flexibilities
OL,16,Fsuch as purchasing credits from rival
OL,17,Fcompanies.
