OL,3,CCar plant boss warns production could
OL,4,C'stop' without Government electric
OL,5,Cpromise
OL,7,FSpeaking at an event hosted by the
OL,8,FSociety of Motor Manufacturers and
OL,9,FTraders in central London, Ms Grazia
OL,10,FDavino reportedly said: "In the UK
OL,11,Fthere will be consequences (from the
OL,12,Fpolicy) for sure. Stellantis UK does
OL,13,Fnot stop, but Stellantis production in
OL,14,Fthe UK could stop."
OL,16,FShe added that the next government
OL,17,Fmust "respond" to the need to increase
OL,18,Fdemand for electric vehicles, adding:
OL,19,F"I want to keep the production (in
OL,20,Fthe) UK."
